Async Weather Tracker

Simple weather app using API and async JavaScript.

Takes a city name → fetches real-time data → shows temperature, weather, humidity, and wind speed.

Also stores search history for quick access.

⚙️ Features
City-based weather search
Real-time API data
Temperature, humidity, wind speed
Search history (click to reuse)
🛠️ Tech Used
HTML
CSS
JavaScript
Fetch API
Async / Await
🚀 How it works
Enter city name
Click submit
Data is fetched from API
UI updates instantly
Search gets stored below
🔑 Setup
Get API key from OpenWeather
Replace API key in JS file:
appid=YOUR_API_KEY
Run the project
⚠️ Note

Basic project.
No frameworks.
Focused on understanding async flow and API handling.

📌 Future Improvements
Error handling (city not found)
Loading indicator
Better UI
Save history with localStorage
